$ Data profiling

Data profiling: analyze and examine data in order to understand the data better.

Data profilig does not rectify data quality problems but it might be a step into this direction.

{ Tools

  Some free data profling tools are
    • → https://datacleaner.github.io/[DataCleaner] Tool
    • → https://sourceforge.net/projects/dataquality[Aggregate Profile Tool] (→ development/languages/Java)
    • Talend Open Studio for Data Quality

  Some commercial tools are
    • Informatica Data Profiling
    • SAP Information Steward
    • Oracle Enterprise Data Quality
    • Collibra Data Stewardship Manager
    • IBM InfoSphere Information Analyzer
    • SAS DataFlux Data Management Studio

}

